nodes.text: A clone who served as a shock trooper with the Coruscant Guard accompanied Commander Stone and several other troopers of the Diplomatic Escort Group with Senator Kharrus and Representative Jar Jar Binks to Florrum. He survived the crash of their shuttle and with the death of Kharrus, was skeptical about Binks's ability to lead the group. He along with all other clones survived the mission and departed Florrum aboard the Twilight.
